<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Horizon UI | Lab 13</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;500;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-accent: #6366f1;
            --secondary-accent: #f43f5e;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            /* Vibrant Mesh Gradient Background */
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3 0%, #e0e7ff 50%, #d1fae5 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #1e293b;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Glassmorphism Navbar */
        .navbar {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) !important;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            padding: 1rem 0;
        }

        .navbar-brand { font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary-accent) !important; font-size: 1.6rem; }

        /* Hero Section with Animation */
        .hero-section {
            padding: 120px 0 80px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #ec4899);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* Catchy Gradient Buttons */
        .btn-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6366f1, #a855f7);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
            color: white;
        }

        /* Soft Glass Cards */
        .card {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 2rem;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Floating Breadcrumb */
        .breadcrumb {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            display: inline-flex;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .breadcrumb-item a { color: var(--primary-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }

        /* Modern Form Inputs */
        .form-control {
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
            border-color: var(--primary-accent);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 80px;
            padding: 40px 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light sticky-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">VIVID<span style="color: #f43f5e;">LABS</span></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#mainNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mainNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto align-items-center">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link px-3 active" href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                        <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle px-3" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">Labs</a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu border-0 shadow-lg mt-3">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">Web Design</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#">UI/UX Tools</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item ms-lg-3">
                        <a class="btn btn-outline-dark rounded-pill px-4" href="#contact">Contact Me</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                    <ol class="breadcrumb">
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Main</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="#">Practicals</a></li>
                        <li class="breadcrumb-item active">No. 13</li>
                    </ol>
                </nav>
            </div>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Pixel Horizon </h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">Crafted with modern CSS techniques and Bootstrap 5 components for an elite experience.</p>
            <button class="btn btn-custom" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#welcomeModal">Explore Features</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                    <div class="display-6 mb-3 text-primary">🎨</div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Dynamic Colors</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Moving away from monochrome to a vibrant, multi-layered mesh gradient aesthetic.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                    <div class="display-6 mb-3 text-danger">📱</div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Pure Response</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Optimized for every screen—from small smartphones to large engineering monitors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                    <div class="display-6 mb-3 text-success">🚀</div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Clean Code</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted">Structured perfectly for GitHub, ensuring fast load times and high readability.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="contact" class="row mt-5 pt-5 justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="card border-0">
                    <h2 class="text-center fw-bold mb-4">Start a Project</h2>
                    <form>
                        <div class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label class="form-label fw-bold small">NAME</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Twinkle">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label class="form-label fw-bold small">EMAIL</label>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control" placeholder="twinkle@student.com">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <label class="form-label fw-bold small">MESSAGE</label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" rows="4" placeholder="How can I help you today?"></textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-custom w-100 mt-4">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="modal fade" id="welcomeModal" tabindex="-1">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
            <div class="modal-content border-0 shadow-lg" style="border-radius: 25px;">
                <div class="modal-header border-0 bg-light rounded-top-4 p-4">
                    <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold">Lab Component Insight</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body p-4">
                    This practical demonstrates the core Bootstrap UI kit:
                    <ul class="mt-3">
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Interactive Dropdowns:</strong> Seamless navigation.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Breadcrumbs:</strong> Clear site hierarchy.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Responsive Grid:</strong> 12-column flexibility.</li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><strong>Modal Systems:</strong> Focused user interaction.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-footer border-0 p-4">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-light rounded-pill" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center">
        <p class="text-muted small">&copy; 2026 Engineering Lab Series | Created by Yash</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>